'''可可饼'''（{{lang-en|Cocoa Solids}}）是从经过烘烤的[[可可豆|可可豆]]研磨成液态的[[可可液|可可液]]中提取[[可可脂|可可脂]]后剩余的成分。被提取出来的可可脂占可可豆重量的50%至57%，赋予巧克力特有的熔化特性。'''可可粉'''（{{lang-en|Cocoa Powder}}）是可可饼作为最终产品出售的固体粉末形式。

可可粉含有[[黄烷-3-醇|黄烷醇]][[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]，如果将可可进行减酸碱化处理，其含量会减少。<ref name="Alkalization">{{Cite journal|title=Impact of Alkalization on the Antioxidant and Flavanol Content of Commercial Cocoa Powders|first=Kenneth B.|last2=Jeffery Hurst|first2=William|journal=Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry|issue=18|doi=10.1021/jf801670p|year=2008|volume=56|pages=8527–8533|pmid=18710243|last3=Payne|first3=Mark J.|last4=Stuart|first4=David A.|last5=Apgar|first5=Joan|last6=Sweigart|first6=Daniel S.|last7=Ou|first7=Boxin|last1=Miller}}</ref>可可中的黄酮类化合物对健康有益。<ref name="science direct">{{Cite journal|title=Cocoa and chocolate flavonoids: Implications for cardiovascular health|last=Steinberg|first=F. M.|last2=Bearden|first2=M. N.|journal=Journal of the American Dietetic Association|issue=2|doi=10.1053/jada.2003.50028|year=2003|volume=103|pages=215–223|pmid=12589329|last3=Keen|first3=C. L.}}</ref>

== 物理性质 ==
[[File:Dutch_process_and_natural_cocoa.jpg|缩略图]]
天然可可粉呈浅褐色，[[pH值|pH值]]为5.3～5.8。<ref name="Alkalization" />经过碱化加工的可可粉颜色较深，为棕红色到接近黑色，pH值为6.8～8.1。碱化后减少了可可的苦味，提高了溶解度，这对可可粉应用于饮料产品发挥了重要作用。上述pH值均在可以安全食用的范围内。<ref>[http://www.flexicon.com/Materials-Handled/Cocoa-Powder.html Materials Handled Cocoa Powder: Overview] {{Wayback|url=http://www.flexicon.com/Materials-Handled/Cocoa-Powder.html |date=20140407094239 }}. Retrieved: 2 April 2014.</ref>

