可可粉含有多种矿物质，包括[[钙|钙]]、[[铜|铜]]、[[镁|镁]]、[[磷|磷]]、[[钾|钾]]、[[钠|钠]]和[[锌|锌]]。所有这些矿物质在可可粉中的含量都高于可可脂和巧克力浆。<ref name="science direct" />每100克可可粉含有约230毫克[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]和2.057克[[可可碱|可可碱]]，而可可豆的其他产品大多不含这些成分。<ref>{{Cite web|title=USDA National Nutrient Database for Standard Reference, Release 24, (2011)|url=http://ndb.nal.usda.gov/ndb/foods/show/6195|access-date=2021-01-01|archive-date=2019-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323211007/https://ndb.nal.usda.gov/ndb/foods/show/6195|dead-url=no}}</ref>可可粉还含有{{tsl|en|clovamide||clovamide}} (N-caffeoyl-L-DOPA)。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Antioxidative Polyphenols Isolated from Theobroma cacao|first=Chiaki|last2=Osakabe|first2=Naomi|journal=Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry|issue=2|doi=10.1021/jf970575o|year=1998|volume=46|pages=454–457|pmid=10554262|last3=Natsume|first3=Midori|last4=Takizawa|first4=Toshio|last5=Gomi|first5=Shuichi|last6=Osawa|first6=Toshihiko|last1=Sanbongi}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Roasting impact on the contents of clovamide (''N''-caffeoyl-''L''-DOPA) and the antioxidant activity of cocoa beans (''Theobroma cacao'' L.)|first=Marco|last2=Locatelli|first2=Monica|journal=Food Chemistry|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.foodchem.2007.07.009|year=2008|volume=106|pages=967–975|last3=Travaglia|first3=Fabiano|last4=Coïsson|first4=Jean-Daniel|last5=Del Grosso|first5=Erika|last6=Minassi|first6=Alberto|last1=Arlorio}}</ref>

=== 黄酮类化合物 ===
{{main|{{tsl|en|Health effects of chocolate|巧克力对健康的影响}}}}
可可粉含有丰富的[[黄酮类化合物|黄酮类化合物]]，该化合物的含量取决于可可粉的加工和制造过程。<ref name="science direct" />碱化会使其黄酮类化合物的含量大大降低。<ref name="Alkalization" /><ref name="Consumerlab">{{Cite web|title=Product Review: Cocoa Powders, Dark Chocolate, Extracts, Nibs, & Supplements|url=https://www.consumerlab.com/reviews/Cocoa_Powders_and_Chocolates_Sources_of_Flavanols/cocoa-flavanols/|date=2014-05-17|publisher=ConsumerLab.com LLC|website=ConsumerLab.com|access-date=2015-02-10|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813003846/https://www.consumerlab.com/reviews/Cocoa_Powders_and_Chocolates_Sources_of_Flavanols/cocoa-flavanols/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Chocolate Terms|url=http://www.thenibble.com/reviews/main/chocolate/glossary.asp#d|publisher=Thenibble.com|access-date=2013-05-27|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033350/http://www.thenibble.com/reviews/main/chocolate/glossary.asp#d|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 安全性 ==
可可粉可能含有[[镉|镉]]。镉是一种有毒的重金属和潜在的[[致癌物|致癌物]]，在一些可可生产地的土壤中发现天然的镉含量很高。2019年1月1日起，[[欧盟|欧盟]]规定了每克可可粉中镉的不得超过0.6微克，以及每克可可含量大于等于50%的[[巧克力|巧克力]]中镉的不得超过0.8微克。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Commission Regulation (EU) No 488/2014 of 12 May 2014: Amending Regulation (EC) No 1881/2006 as regards maximum levels of cadmium in foodstuffs|url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/PDF/?uri=CELEX:32014R0488&from=EN|date=2014-05-12|access-date=2016-08-22|archive-date=2018-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824034055/https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/PDF/?uri=CELEX:32014R0488&from=EN|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[加拿大|加拿大]]，对于一个体重68千克的人，每天摄入天然保健品的镉含量不得超过6微克。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Quality of natural health products guide|url=http://www.hc-sc.gc.ca/dhp-mps/consultation/natur/consult_quality-qualite-eng.php#a3.2|access-date=2016-08-22|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018153200/http://www.hc-sc.gc.ca/dhp-mps/consultation/natur/consult_quality-qualite-eng.php#a3.2|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然[[美国政府|美国政府]]没有对食品或保健品中的镉含量进行限制，但[[加州|加州]]规定了每天口服镉的不得超过4. 1微克，并规定每日每份产品的镉含量超过此量的产品必须在外包装上发出警告。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Proposition 65 Maximum Allowable Daily Level (MADL) for Reproductive Toxicity for Cadmium (Oral Route)|url=http://www.oehha.ca.gov/media/downloads/proposition-65/chemicals/cadmium20madlfinal.pdf|access-date=2016-08-22|archive-date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209235423/http://oehha.ca.gov/media/downloads/proposition-65/chemicals/cadmium20madlfinal.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

